wt config state marker - Branch markers

Usage: [1m[36mwt config state marker[0m [36m[OPTIONS][0m [36m[COMMAND][0m

[1m[32mCommands:[0m
  [1m[36mget[0m    Get marker for a branch
  [1m[36mset[0m    Set marker for a branch
